Having considered the report of the Working Group on Jurisdictional Immunities of States and Their Property of the International Law Commission, set forth in the annex to the report of the Commission on the work of its fifty-first session,Official Records of the General Assembly, Fifty-fourth Session, Supplement No 10 and corrigenda (A/54/10 and Corr.1 and 2).
