7. Also requests the Secretary-General to report to the General Assembly at its fifty-sixth session on the implementation of the present resolution;
8. Decides to include in the provisional agenda of its fifty-sixth session the item entitled "United Nations Regional Centre for Peace, Disarmament and Development in Latin America and the Caribbean".
